About Us
Our Story
Zephyrhills Golf Course has been a cornerstone of the Zephyrhills community since its establishment in 1957.
With over six decades of history, our course has provided a welcoming and challenging environment for golfers of all skill levels.
Book A Tee Time
Our Course
Our 18-hole course features 5,054 yards of golf from the longest tees for a par of 68. With a course rating of 70.0 and a slope rating of 113, it offers a unique blend of challenge and playability.
Whether you’re a seasoned golfer or a beginner, you’ll find our course both enjoyable and rewarding.
Our Mission
At Zephyrhills Golf Course, our mission is to provide an exceptional golfing experience for all our guests. We are committed to maintaining the highest standards of course conditions and customer service.
Our goal is to create a friendly and inclusive atmosphere where everyone feels welcome. Contact us for more information.
